folder: Parkside Avenue & Rogers Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Parkside Avenue, at the northwest corner of Rogers Avenue, showing Public School No. 92. This shows the old school building on Rogers Avenue. The new building fronts on Park-side Avenue.
